Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:07.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:46.96,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,To Help Somebody Someday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:10.92,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,We can't handle something that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:15.52,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, we have to \Nget the kids out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:23.62,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, take turns riding out of here on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.24,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:28.68,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:34.52,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take at least ten or twenty \Nminutes to get them all out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.94,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hold this thing back until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get near them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:48.54,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Die... All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.67,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,B-Baro? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.55,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.65,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:21.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taken responsibility \Nfor any of this yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you die until you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:28.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Also, what's your problem? \NYou're trying to kill your own brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:35.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my sword's working, \Nso I'm just gonna quickly take care of—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:43.31,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Now your anti-magic won't be \Nable to defeat him so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:47.60,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,The dark magic item I just injected \Nhim with eats the subject's life force
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.52,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,and produces an explosion of magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.92,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.08,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:15.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:20.88,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you got in the way again! \NQuit butting in, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.01,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in an old \Nlady whose magic's all dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.22,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got a mouth \Non you, whippersnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:32.17,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that as you get older, the magic \Nyou can generate internally weakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:35.67,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But the power to work with \Nthe mana that dwells
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.85,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,in nature can be increased at any age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:43.86,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I have years of experience and technique. \NI won't lose to a youngster like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.24,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate us old hags!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:50.11,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're an annoying \Nold lady, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.79,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you kick the bucket today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.29,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.41,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That being said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:03.03,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight well while protecting \Nthe kids as they escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.30,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. This is only going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.05,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Curse that Gauche! How could \Nhe run off like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.82,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.04,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm taking you back into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.17,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not only does my magic \Nnot work on that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but an insanely powerful \Nmagical monster appeared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.18,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in danger if I fight that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.50,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:32.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to the others, \Nas long as you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.87,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Who cares about anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:43.67,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The House of Adlai is a distinguished \Nnoble family that anyone would envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:47.59,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Little Gauche looks as \Ndignified as his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:51.16,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,And little Marie is as \Nbeautiful as her mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:58.37,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, about you helping me with my business...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:03.69,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mother and Father are dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:09.05,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They were attacked by some \Nrobbers after leaving my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.70,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's written in their will that they left
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.76,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,their fortune and everything \Nthey owned to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.33,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Every last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.16,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.54,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you guys—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:21.71,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.35,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.51,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What an impudent brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.22,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.03,flashback,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Bubby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.06,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:42.85,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Marie, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.02,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So as I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.02,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.14,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie is everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.62,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.19,flashback,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:07:00.58,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Marie is smiling,\NI don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.91,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all the cash you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.67,flashback,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:09.79,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And? Nobles should help out the needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.84,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Only Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:13.88,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.91,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be paying for all of your crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.06,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You think I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.78,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:36.87,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care about other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.89,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:48.71,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I hate having a big brother who's so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.53,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:58.20,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that a lot of people \Ndid some awful things to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.97,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But Sister and the kids at \Nthe church are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:07.48,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I wasn't lonely when you \Nweren't with me was because of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.84,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you became a Magic Knight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:15.64,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's lives are connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.12,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,We're who we are because they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.67,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:28.21,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's your job as a \NMagic Knight to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:32.22,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really proud that you're a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:35.22,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please just be the cool \Nbig brother I'm proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.41,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:41.01,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:42.85,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.81,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.61,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Sister and Asta saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.02,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,That's so like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.15,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, that robe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:09:00.49,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Asta lent it to me so I wouldn't feel lonely \Nwhile he went to go save everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:03.79,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,He said it had the courage \Nof a Magic Knight in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:09.18,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I'll wait here with Marco.\NPlease go save everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:12.34,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Marie! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:15.44,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better mean that,\Nyou stupid little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:18.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay if anything happens to Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.67,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.35,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.11,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.11,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.06,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.51,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.48,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.04,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get away with Sister's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:35.23,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Asta protected us, but that \Nmonster's really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:39.11,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay! My brother's \Ngoing to fight with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:42.58,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's a Magic Knight \Njust like Asta, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.76,main,Kid 1,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.68,main,Kid 2,0000,0000,0000,,So he must be really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.79,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.80,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, make sure you stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.84,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.87,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.87,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.68,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta this, Asta that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.31,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about that shrimp, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.48,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The captain and the other squad \Nmembers wouldn't shut up about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.06,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but he immediately got caught by that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:17.87,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I'm sure he and that \Nold hag gave up and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:23.74,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it,\Npeople only care about themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:42.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet... I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.58,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:49.10,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop protecting them \Nand let me catch you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:54.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop protecting them? I'm a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance! Even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.99,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Is he... actually that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:11.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop protecting them? I'm a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance! Even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:20.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not going to die until \NI become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.58,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! On your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:27.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You yelled something stupid \Nlike "I'm not going to die,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,and then you actually almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:33.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche! Why'd you run off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.79,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:41.32,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't run. I only helped Marie escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.45,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,He finally came back, that fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.78,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.37,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.79,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You joining in isn't going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I'm going to fight... \Nfor the sake of Marie's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.19,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And so she'll say I'm cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Real Double!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.09,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Double Refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:25.91,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This monster... Magic keeps bubbling up \Nfrom it, and it regenerates immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:31.09,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:33.33,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My magic isn't even touching that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:37.83,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been this incompatible \Nwith an opponent since the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.14,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Should I use my trump card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:44.27,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No... No matter how strong my \Nmirror magic becomes, it won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.07,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,How lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you came to help! What are\Nyou doing charging in all by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I protect you! You protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be able to fight forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,An epic strategy, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:27.09,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of half-baked strategy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.71,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This guy really is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.52,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, {\i0}he{\i1} was \Npretty half-baked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:40.23,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to keep going? \NYou're not gonna be able to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.83,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.03,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:51.81,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she's that important, \Njoin my squad and support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.57,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.32,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an escaped convict!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.49,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? And?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:05.31,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And? I don't trust others, \Nand I only think about my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.83,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:12.43,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just protect what you want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.76,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that'll help somebody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:21.56,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, did you know this \Nwould happen someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, how many kids are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.90,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.67,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie will be sad if you all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.21,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Did Gauche just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you acting all tough for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're teammates! What else would we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:54.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid little brat! You need to \Nlearn how to talk to your seniors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And something's shining over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:32.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man! Even that didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:38.02,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what was that? A flying \Nanti-magic slash attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.83,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do it? How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.66,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to defeat that monster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:46.90,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,is to hit it with so many attacks at once\Nthat it doesn't have time to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.67,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The most effective strike was \Nthe slash Asta just hit it with,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.86,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but he can't launch enough of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.60,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if I used\Nmy magic on someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:03.09,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because Gauche had always preferred \Nto act alone and didn't trust others,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:07.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he'd never thought of using his \Nmagic to support someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:13.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But due to his past failures and his \Nreluctant acknowledgment of Asta,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he was able to create a spell that was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,fundamentally similar, \Nyet completely different,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and engraved a new page in his grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:26.64,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't be able to activate this \Nspell with the magic I have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me a little time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.05,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn how to treat old hags.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.91,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only last a minute, so make it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:48.14,main,sally,0000,0000,0000,,Leftover magic like that \Nisn't going to work at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:51.59,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Asta! Do that thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me! \NIf I could, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.65,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw. How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:08.56,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice. I've been hiding \Nthis, but I'll have to use it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:10.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:19.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the magic accumulated in \Nthe mirror magic item in my left eye
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,to activate the new spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.36,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:30.96,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:48.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:01.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.50,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.19,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:23.51,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that he had all \Nof his life force sucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.85,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Baro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.29,flashback,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.63,flashback,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep crying, Neige?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.61,flashback,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.11,flashback,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Baro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:54.40,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Baro, I won't forgive her for \Nturning you into this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.59,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,But the one I can't forgive most of all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:01.76,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,is myself for leaving everything to \Nhim and just doing what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:08.75,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said, I haven't taken \Nresponsibility for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:13.40,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to pay for both of our crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:17.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And when you're done \Nwith that, let's be buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:21.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can use really cool magic, \Nso you'd be really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.07,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Thank—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.72,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What is this immense magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.93,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt something this huge—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.18,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't... see a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:54.96,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:59.48,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,A new enemy? Are they attacking \Neverything in sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.36,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.75,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.13,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.13,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They got what they deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:26.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that appeared \Nat the enemy's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.57,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:33.39,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the Eye \Nof the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.39,sign_29665_280_Leader_of_the_Ey,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun\N{\fs30}Licht
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.39,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:37.60,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.97,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A four-leaf clover grimoire... \NJust like Yuno's?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:23.50,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:22.95,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.96,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Marie's in Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's in Danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,All right, one, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:32.56,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie! Are you an angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:34.39,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything when Marie's around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:39.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But there are times where I must steel \Nmy heart and decline Marie's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:40.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,For example!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:45.41,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, go back and save \NAsta and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:48.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! Going back would put you in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:53.19,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! I want to eat some \Nhot, extra-cheesy doria!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! Eating that would put \Nyour tongue in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:58.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You'll burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:02.23,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, doesn't lying \Nout in the sun feel nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:06.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! If you're in the sun too long, \Nyour skin will be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:09.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,UV rays are a fearsome enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.38,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, show me a really cool spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:15.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No... Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:18.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:21.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:24.27,main,Maries,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:29.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No... Now I'm... in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:34.21,main,Maries,0000,0000,0000,,Brother? Brother? Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:38.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy who was at the \NEye of the Midnight Sun hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:42.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who attacked the Clover \NKingdom and did that to Captain Fuegoleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:43.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:47.65,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 34: \N"Light Magic vs. Dark Magic."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:50.14,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 34\N\N{\fs18} Light Magic VS Dark Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.43,0:23:49.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
